FT  23 MAR 94 / World Stock Markets: South Africa
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Gold posted gains as the sector remained buoyed by a strong bullion
performance. But industrials were lower amid a lack of foreign interest. The
gold index lost 41 at 2,121, industrials shed 43 to 6,067 and the overall
rose 1 to 5,231.
