</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By JOHN SIMKINS
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
Sogefi, Italy's listed car components company controlled by Mr Carlo De
Benedetti's CIR holding company, yesterday reported net group profits of
L18.1bn (Dollars 10.7m) for 1993, down from L33.3bn the previous year,
writes John Simkins.
