FT  23 MAR 94 / UK Company News: Berry Starquest
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Berry Starquest, an investment trust, had a net asset value per share of
239.6p at the year ended January 31, against 200.1p six months earlier and
170.7p at the previous year end.
Net revenue for the year fell from Pounds 160,000 to Pounds 126,000 for
earnings per share of 2.4p (3.1p). An unchanged dividend of 2.2p is
proposed.
</TEXT>
<XX>
