<HEADLINE>
FT  22 MAR 94 / Survey of Jersey (15): Guide for visitors - Useful Contacts
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By SUE STUART
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
Some useful contacts in the business and public sectors:
Regulators: Richard Syvret, Financial Services Dept. tel. 79111. States
Greffe (clerk): Royal Square, St. Helier - tel. 73060. Income Tax: Cyril Le
Marquand House, St. Helier - tel. 79111. Customs: Caladonia Place, St.
Helier - tel. 73561. Immigration: Conway Street, St. Helier  - tel. 21441.
Police HQ: Rouge Bouillon, St. Helier - tel. 75511. Telecoms: Jersey
Telecoms - tel. 75846. Newspaper: Jersey Evening Post  - tel. 73333. Estate
Agents: Healey &amp; Baker - tel. 71441. Hamptons, Gothard &amp; Trevor - tel.
72617. Jersey Fund Managers Association: Richard Wilkinson - tel. 73114.
Jersey Bankers Association: Julian Bub  - tel. 25561. Institute of Chartered
Secretaries and Administrators: R. D. Ellis - tel. 79500. Society of
